            </p>
            <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[-0.03em] text-slate-900 lg:text-[32px]">
              Explore Airlines
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p className="hidden max-w-md text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500 lg:block">
